text:

It is worthwhile to use two “#” for headings and three “#” for subheadings to that the live table of the contents on the right hand side of the deployed website allows easy navigation among sections.

title: Content Creators
text: This workshop was created and facilitated by a dynamic team that is here to assist you before, during, and after your attendance at the workshop! To learn a bit more about us, see our bios and relevant links below.

title: Content Creators
text:
Person Name
personal website link –  GitHub profile –  @Twitter handle – contact email
Remove any sections of the above bar of contact info / links that a given workshop instructor doesn’t want to include. There should be a short (2-4 sentence) blurb that lets workshop attendees get a sense for who you are and tells them how to get in contact with you. Copy paste this block for each person who created workshop content and/or facilitated the workshop in person or via videoconference.
